---
/**
 * context-engineering 0008 · Figure 5 — Module 3 "the ingestion pipeline":
 * load → parse → chunk → embed → upsert, with embed flagged as the per-token
 * cost stage.
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from
 * docs/context-engineering/lessons/0008-embeddings-indexing-and-cost.html.
 * Lives as an .astro component (not inline MDX) because raw inline SVG with
 * kebab-case attributes is unreliable in MDX but is plain HTML in .astro.
 *
 * The pipeline arrows reference the shared #arw (fill #6b675f) and #arwM
 * (fill #b5179e) markers, declared once in the source's top-of-body <defs>. The
 * MDX has no such block, so both markers are inlined here.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 640 150"
        role="img"
        aria-label="Documents flow through load, parse, chunk, embed, and upsert into the vector store."
    >
        <defs>
            <marker
                id="arw"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#6b675f"></path></marker
            >
            <marker
                id="arwM"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#b5179e"></path></marker
            >
        </defs>
        <rect x="14" y="50" width="96" height="46" rx="8" fill="#efe7f0" stroke="#111110"
        ></rect><text
            x="62"
            y="78"
            text-anchor="middle"
            font-size="10"
            font-weight="700"
            fill="#111110">Load</text
        >
        <rect x="140" y="50" width="96" height="46" rx="8" fill="#efe7f0" stroke="#111110"
        ></rect><text
            x="188"
            y="78"
            text-anchor="middle"
            font-size="10"
            font-weight="700"
            fill="#111110">Parse</text
        >
        <rect x="266" y="50" width="96" height="46" rx="8" fill="#efe7f0" stroke="#111110"
        ></rect><text
            x="314"
            y="78"
            text-anchor="middle"
            font-size="10"
            font-weight="700"
            fill="#111110">Chunk</text
        >
        <rect
            x="392"
            y="50"
            width="96"
            height="46"
            rx="8"
            fill="#f1eef2"
            stroke="#b5179e"
            stroke-width="2"></rect><text
            x="440"
            y="72"
            text-anchor="middle"
            font-size="10"
            font-weight="700"
            fill="#b5179e">Embed</text
        ><text x="440" y="86" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8" fill="#6b675f">costs tokens</text>
        <rect x="518" y="50" width="108" height="46" rx="8" fill="#e9f3ec" stroke="#2f5d3a"
        ></rect><text
            x="572"
            y="72"
            text-anchor="middle"
            font-size="10"
            font-weight="700"
            fill="#2f5d3a">Upsert</text
        ><text x="572" y="86" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8" fill="#6b675f">to the store</text>
        <line x1="110" y1="73" x2="138" y2="73" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
        <line x1="236" y1="73" x2="264" y2="73" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
        <line x1="362" y1="73" x2="390" y2="73" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
        <line x1="488" y1="73" x2="516" y2="73" stroke="#b5179e" marker-end="url(#arwM)"></line>
        <text x="320" y="28" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#111110"
            >Ingestion: source &rarr; vectors in the store</text
        >
        <text x="320" y="124" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" font-style="italic" fill="#6b675f"
            >re-run incrementally as data changes — not once at launch</text
        >
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        Five stages, one of which (embed) bills you per token. The pipeline must re-run on change —
        incrementally for edited docs, fully when the model or chunking strategy changes — or the
        store drifts out of sync with reality.<sup><a href="#s2" id="r6b">2</a></sup>
    </figcaption>
</figure>
